a just in time compiler for the exo language.

learn about exo: https://github.com/exo-lang/exo/blob/main/docs/README.md

usage:

    $ uv run exojit examples/demo.py --mlir
    $ uv run exojit examples/demo.py --asm
    $ uv run exojit examples/demo.py --c
    $ uv run python examples/demo.py # jit

how it works:

      Exo Python source
          v
      Exo LoopIR
          v
    - - - - - - - - - - - - - xDSL
      MLIR module
          v
      MLIR LLVM dialect
          v
    - - - - - - - - - - - - - llvmlite MCJIT
      Native code
